title: Carrie Vaughn - Kitty Norville Series 1-11
description:
Kitty Norville is the main character of a series of novels by Carrie Vaughn. She is a werewolf who hosts a popular syndicated radio phone-in show based in Denver called "The Midnight Hour". The program focuses on supernatural issues.

The only rip in this collection that is mine is Book 10 - it is among my first - please let me know if there are any issues.  Converted using SoundTaxi 128kbps

My thanks to the original uploaders for the rest of the series.
